title: Drake's Hotline Bling peaks with mashup of Wolfe Tones
text:
That's it. We're done now.
You can stop with the Hotline Bling parodies because nothing - and we mean NOTHING - is going to top this. It literally can't.
Josh Concannon managed to sync up Drake's Hotline Bling with Wolfe Tones' Celtic Symphony to create... this.
Take a look.
i never would of taught these would go together so perfectly... full song in the link for anyones that lookinghttps://youtu.be/8O8e3SeJo_8
Posted by Josh Concannon on Friday, 23 October 2015
Good night, Internet. You can all go home now.
G'luck now.
